ꔷ A gravimetric feature almost parallel and near the Paraná River indicates the presence of an anomalous deep body.
ꔷ We have presented a 2-D geoelectric model of the deep structure in the Paraná Basin.
ꔷ Presence of a high conductivity band in the upper part, that represents the sedimentary basin.
ꔷ High resistivity body below the area of the basin.
ꔷ Our model may help to understand the geological structure of the Paraná Basin.
